window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The Complete series in a single offering!</b></p> <p>Delve Deep, Rise High</p> <p>Kuno, a former soldier, is searching for fortune. But not just as any ordinary adventurer. True power comes from making alliances with the alluring dungeon goddesses. Armed with a mysterious journal, his trusty axes, and no small amount of courage, he must navigate treacherous dungeons and prove his worth.</p> <p>The prize? Exclusive access to the goddesses' domains.</p> <p>With each goddess offering unique challenges and tantalizing rewards, will Kuno forge the alliances he needs to uncover a legendary hidden treasure?</p> <p>Outwit his foes. Win the goddesses' favor. Assemble a band of powerful allies to become the ultimate Dungeon God.</p>"; 
